revision.text: ==English== ===Etymology=== Borrowed from {{bor|en|cmn|熊|tr=xióng}}. ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Xiongs}} # {{surname|en}}. ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Xiong'' is the 929<sup>th</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 37499 individuals. ''Xiong'' is most common among Asian/Pacific Islander (98.07%) individuals.
